latestPosts.caption:
Dreaming as high as possible is what we've been told to do when we're younger, but we take time for granted just like our Health.
As we get older, we start spending our lives instead of living it. 

Sitting still is boring cause we're addicted to music or maybe stillness is painful cause it makes us aware of the noises of our consciousness. 

Becoming aware of our desires and making avatars of it to find out which one could be the best - is a gift that humans are bearing, we better make something out of it.
